text: This obsoletes IRM 25.15.16, Relief from Joint and Several Liability, Telephone Contacts.

The material relating to Telephone Contacts for Cincinnati Centralized Innocent Spouse Operation (CCISO) has been updated and incorporated into new IRM 25.15.18.9.2, Phones. IRM 25.15.18, Innocent Spouse Processing Procedures, went into effect July 11, 2016.
25.15.16, Telephone Contacts, dated July 30, 2014 is obsolete as of the date of this
Employees in Cincinnati Centralized Innocent Spouse Operation (CCISO) who will have phone contact with customers regarding innocent spouse claims.
